{"_path":"/clean-arch/chapter14","_dir":"clean-arch","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"14 元件耦合性","description":"本章介紹三個元件之間該有的原則：","pageTitle":"Chapter 14 元件耦合性","contributors":["frank30941"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本章介紹三個元件之間該有的原則："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相依要無環"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相依要穩定"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"抽象介面要穩定"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"影響架構的作用力有三種：政治力、技術能力和揮發力"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"無環依賴原則the-acyclic-dependencies-principle-adp"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"無環依賴原則(The Acyclic Dependencies Principle, ADP)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"簡單說就是元件相依有向圖中，不得出現環"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"那這個原則是怎麼演化而來的呢？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"很久很久以前，所有的工程師都編輯相同的一份程式碼，而他們都面臨一個「一覺醒來，發現自己在異世界」的問題。昨天下班前寫的程式明明是正常運作，怎麼早上來上班就壞了？！這是因為有人半夜連ＶＰＮ，修改了同一份的程式碼，意外地，把你昨天寫的東西弄壞了。\n為了解決這個夢魘，有識之士提出了 Ｗeekly Build 週建置\n星期一到星期四，人們在自己的機器上開發，避免編輯到同一份原始碼；星期五的時候，大家將各自的原始碼合併，然後建置新版的程式。因此，人們有四天可以專心開發，再也沒有「起床症候群」的困擾了。當專案很小或是人數很少的時候，大家過著幸福快樂的日子。可惜好景不常，一旦專案越來越大、人越來越多，合併原始碼所需的時間便越拉越長，單單星期五一天處理不完，於是建置時間從星期五、星期四漸漸的往週中延長。於是，時間都拿去處理合併，開發時間被壓縮自然地效率越降越低。\n很顯然週建置還不足以解決問題。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"消除依賴還"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"消除依賴還"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"首先我們要把整個開發分解成一個個的小元件，而且每個元件必須是單人或一組可以負責做完的工作份量。當元件穩定的時候，開發團隊釋出負責的元件並附上版號，讓別人使用釋出的版本，同時間，開發團隊可持續開發也不會影響到使用該元件的程式碼。\n如此一來，當別人釋出新的元件的時候，你可以選擇相依舊的或是新的元件，再也不會因為別人的改動讓你的程式壞掉了！我們解決了之前週建置遇到的問題："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"別人修改的程式導致你的功能壞掉"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不需要統一時間合併程式碼"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"但這個前提是"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相依有向圖裡面不可以有環"}]},{"type":"text","value":"！否則還是會發生「起床症候群」。\n下圖的相依有向圖中，沒有任何的環。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"align":"center"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"/code-study/images/clean-arch/14/01.png","width":"50%"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"從相依有向圖，我們可以很清楚地解釋出元件的時候會對誰造成影響"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Case: Release "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"main"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在釋出新版的"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"main"}]},{"type":"text","value":"的時候，我們完全不用擔心會影響到其他的元件"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Case: Release "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Presenters"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"更新 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Presenters"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 會影響"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"main"}]},{"type":"text","value":" & "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"view"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，這兩個元件的開發者可以自己決定要不要跟著升級"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相反的，在開發的時候只要確保相依的套件的版本是對的，就可以保證元件的功能可以正常運作。換句話說，開發者無須考慮全部的元件，只需要專注在相依的元件上即可。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"當我們要釋出應用程式或是 linbrary 的時候，由底層向上層建置即可，建置程序非常的清晰明瞭。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"如果有環會造成什麼影響"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果有環會造成什麼影響"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果 Entities 相依於 Authorizer，使得相依有向圖變成下圖，會發生什麼事？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"align":"center"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"/code-study/images/clean-arch/14/02.png","width":"50%"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"對於 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Database"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 來說，相依變多導致釋出 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Database"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的話，需要考慮的事情變多了"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Entities"}]},{"type":"text","value":", "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Authorizer"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 和 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Interactors"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 等效上，變成了一個新的且龐大的元件"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Entities"}]},{"type":"text","value":", "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Authorizer"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 和 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Interactors"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 之中的任何修改都會相互影響"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不知道要怎麼建置 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Entities"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"那我們要怎麼解決環的問題呢？使用 Dependency Inversion Principle (DIP)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Entities"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 裡面新增 interface "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Permission"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"align":"center"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"/code-study/images/clean-arch/14/03.png","width":"50%"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2. 新增一個元件 `Permission`\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"align":"center"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"/code-study/images/clean-arch/14/04.png","width":"50%"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在開發過程中，我們發現元件結構經常改變，我們要時時刻刻確保有向相依圖中沒有環。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"top-down-design"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Top-Down Design"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經由上面的例子，由上而下的設計模式是不存的。因為元件架構隨著開發的進程逐漸演進，不可能在開始一個專案的時候，就決定好元件的架構。隨著開發進程，我們會開始思考要如何重複利用寫好的原件，於是我們可以用 共同重復使用原則(common reuse principle, CRP) 來實作；當元件變小變多的時候，因為你不清楚別人怎麼使用你的原件，所以出現環狀相依的機率越來越大，而出現環狀相依的時候，我們會用 無環依賴原則(acyclic dependencies principle, ADP) 來解決環狀相依，而解決問題的副作用就是讓元件相依架構圖不穩定、時常改變。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"另一方面，元件相依圖最重要的功能將「維護性」和「可建置性」圖像化。隨著開發我們的元件架構會越變越複雜，我們可以藉由元件相依圖來管理各個模組、元件的相依關係，以避免出現「起床症候群」，要避免「起床症候群」就要"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"各模組、元件內的修改所造成的影響範圍要本地化(越小越好)\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以在實作的時候，需要注意這兩個原則 共同封閉原則(common closure principle, CCP) 和 單一職責(single responsibility principle, SRP)。還有合併會互相影響的原件。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"將系統內某元件經常變動的部分和不常變動的部分分開，讓常變動的元件相依不常變動元件\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這樣才不會因為常變動的部分導致不變的部分壞掉"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"穩定依賴原則sdp"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"穩定依賴原則(SDP)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"朝著穩定的方向進行依賴"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"透過符合共同封閉元則(Common Closure Principle, CCP)，我們會建立對某些變化類型敏感的元件，這些元件被設計成可變的，我們預期它們會變化。\n那麼對於一個預期是可變的元件，他就不應該讓另一個難以更改的元件依賴他，否則就會造原可變的元件難以更改\n這就是軟體的反常的特性，就算你的模組沒有任何的修改，只要別人對你有依賴，就可以讓你的程式變得難以更改。透過遵循 單一職責(single responsibility principle, SRP) 可以確保設計成可變的模組不會被更難以更改的模組所依賴。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"穩定性"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"穩定性"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"直立的硬幣：推倒很簡單 => 穩定性低"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桌子：推倒不簡單 => 穩定性高"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使軟體元件難以變更(變穩定)的因素很多，包括規模、複雜性、清晰程度等等，但我們要來著重在另一種因素，也就是「讓其他元件依賴他」。具有許多輸入依賴關係的元件是很穩定的，因為要使所有依賴它的元件能夠相容變更，往往需要非常大的工作量"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下圖是一個穩定的元件 X，有 3 個元件依賴他，因此就有 3 個理由不去更改他，相反地 X 不被任何元件依賴，所有的外部影響都不會使其改變，我們稱 X 是無依賴性的。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"align":"center"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"/code-study/images/clean-arch/14/05.png","width":"50%"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下圖是一個不穩定的元件，沒有任何元件依賴 Y，且 Y 依賴於 3 個元件，所以它具有 3 個外部更改源，我們稱 Y 是依賴性的"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"align":"center"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"/code-study/images/clean-arch/14/06.png","width":"50%"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"計算穩定性"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"計算穩定性"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FadeIn：輸入依賴度 (被別人依賴)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FadeOut：輸出依賴度 (依賴別人)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I：不穩定性"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"mjx-container","props":{"className":["MathJax"],"jax":"SVG","display":"true"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"svg","props":{"style":"vertical-align: -1.738ex;","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"24.498ex","height":"4.86ex","role":"img","focusable":"false","viewBox":"0 -1380 10828 2148","xmlnsXLink":"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"defs","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"path","props":{"id":"MJX-1-TEX-I-1D43C","d":"M43 1Q26 1 26 10Q26 12 29 24Q34 43 39 45Q42 46 54 46H60Q120 46 136 53Q137 53 138 54Q143 56 149 7